englishTranslationText:
And	He	gave	you	much	of	what	you	seek;	
and	if	you	enumerate	the	favours	of	Allah,	
you	 will	 never	 be	 able	 to	 count	 them;	
indeed	 man	 is	 very	 unjust,	 most	
ungrateful.

So	do	not	ever	assume	that	Allah will	not	
fulfil	His	promise	to	His	Noble	Messengers;	
indeed	Allah is	the	Dominant,	the	Avenger.
